  "text": "In order to detect the most explanatory variables on the presence of a defoliation event, we applied the RF approach for classification problems introduced by [CITATION_1] . Its integrated variable importance measure provides a ranking of the variables according to their explanatory power (see [CITATION_2] . In fact, the RF has been stated to be the best classifier in comparison to a total number of 179 classifiers tested for \"Average Accuracy\" and \"Friedman Ranking\" [CITATION_3] .",
